Hi,

Following patch was enough to solve the problem for my setup in 
google-earth port directory:

--- work/google-earth-5/drivers.ini.orig    2013-04-20 
03:04:44.000000000 +0200
+++ work/google-earth-5/drivers.ini    2013-04-20 03:04:55.000000000 +0200
@@ -97,7 +97,7 @@
      }}
  }

-OS = linux {
+OS = FreeBSD {
      SETTINGS {
          onlyOGL = true
      }


Regards,

-- Cybil
